Body:
I'm trying to install Intel System Studio IoT edition and it keeps failing. Can anyone help fix the error?

"
Maybe the file you downloaded wasn't complete, or your computer has bad RAM?  Try checksumming the file, if Intel publishes checksums for the installer.

I recommend you use the Intel System Studio 2018 Beta, which carries forward the IoT functionality (docker containers) https://software.intel.com/sites/intel-system-studio-2018-beta/#/

"
